==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Palm Sunday
<hw>Palm" Sun`day</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Eccl.)</fld> <def>The Sunday
next before <er>Easter</er>; -- so called in commemoration of the
triumphal entry of Jesus Christ into Jerusalem, when the multitude
strewed palm branches in the way. The event is commemorated in Christian
churches by distribution of blessed palm leaves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Palmy</ent>⟦br⟧
